OL,7,FA retired doctor was beaten to death
OL,8,Fby his own son who absconded from a
OL,9,Fhospital's mental health facility
OL,10,Ffollowing a number of health board
OL,11,Ffailures, a coroner has ruled.
OL,13,FDr Kim Harrison, a renowned chest
OL,14,Fconsultant, was beaten to death by his
OL,15,Fson Daniel Harrison at their family
OL,16,Fhome in Clydach, Swansea, in March
OL,17,F2022.
