OL,3,CFailings found in care of man who
OL,4,Ckilled his father after escaping from
OL,5,Chospital
OL,7,FDr Harrison, 68, was a respected
OL,8,Fdoctor at Swansea Bay University
OL,9,FHealth Board, who the coroner found
OL,10,Ffailed in a number of ways in the care
OL,11,Fof Daniel Harrison before the fatal
OL,12,Fattack.
OL,14,FThey include failing to properly
OL,15,Fassess and diagnose Daniel Harrison,
OL,16,Fpossibly contributing to the fatal
OL,17,Fattack on his father, while the
OL,18,Fconcerns of Daniel Harrison's family
OL,19,Fabout his mental health in the weeks
OL,20,Fand days leading up to the attack were
OL,21,Flargely ignored.
