OL,7,FAn inquest into the death of Dr
OL,8,FHarrison, which concluded on Tuesday,
OL,9,F16 April, was told how Daniel Harrison
OL,10,Fescaped from Neath Port Talbot
OL,11,FHospital by pushing past a nurse at a
OL,12,Fsecurity door, ordering a taxi and
OL,13,Fthen returning to the family home,
OL,14,Fwhere he killed his father.
OL,16,FHe had been diagnosed with paranoid
OL,17,Fschizophrenia and had been detained
OL,18,Funder the Mental Health Act at the
OL,19,Fhospital in the days leading up to the
OL,20,Fattack.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/13
