OL,7,FRecording a narrative conclusion,
OL,8,Fassistant coroner Kirsten Heaven
OL,9,Fraised a number of concerns.
OL,11,FPreviously, Daniel Harrison pleaded
OL,12,Fguilty to manslaughter on the grounds
OL,13,Fof diminished responsibility and was
OL,14,Fmade the subject of a hospital order.
