OL,7,FDr Kim Harrison's wife Jane Harrison
OL,8,Fsaid after the hearing: "This inquest
OL,9,Fhad focused on the events which led to
OL,10,Fthe tragic death of my husband Kim in
OL,11,FApril 2022. It has exposed more
OL,12,Ffailings in the care of our son, Dan,
OL,13,Fby Swansea Bay Health Board and the
OL,14,FCity and County of Swansea.
OL,16,F"As the coroner has made clear, Dan
OL,17,Fsuffered a relapse of his chronic
OL,18,Fschizophrenic illness which was well
OL,19,Fmanaged until he was lost to follow-up
OL,20,Fby the health board in 2018.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G5/13
