OL,4,Ckilled his father after escaping from
OL,5,Chospital
OL,7,F"Our family could not have done more
OL,8,Fto seek help for Dan's deteriorating
OL,9,Fmental health from senior
OL,10,Fpsychologists, social workers and
OL,11,Fmanagers.
OL,13,F"Together with close friends, we
OL,14,Frepeatedly raised concerns and yet to
OL,15,Fthis day we have had no explanation as
OL,16,Fto why our calls were ignored,
OL,17,Fminimised or explained away.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G6/13
