OL,3,CFailings found in care of man who
OL,4,Ckilled his father after escaping from
OL,5,Chospital
OL,7,F"The coroner has recognised the
OL,8,Fdefensive attitude of staff at the
OL,9,Ftime and we were dismayed to see this
OL,10,Fcontinue throughout the inquest.
OL,12,F"We remain at a loss to understand how
OL,13,Fso many professionals could get it so
OL,14,Fwrong, how they could fail to deliver
OL,15,Fbasic medical care and how major
OL,16,Fsystem failings could remain
OL,17,Funaddressed.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G7/13
