OL,3,CFailings found in care of man who
OL,4,Ckilled his father after escaping from
OL,5,Chospital
OL,7,F"What is also apparent is the lack of
OL,8,Faccountability at every level in these
OL,9,Forganisations and this is apparently
OL,10,Fingrained in the culture of the teams
OL,11,Fwho should have been managing Dan's
OL,12,Fcare.
OL,14,F"Culture affects people's behaviour
OL,15,Fand the behaviour in this case fell
OL,16,Fwell below acceptable standards.
OL,18,F"We miss Kim every day. We continue to
OL,19,Fgive Dan our love and support as he
OL,20,Fsteadily recovers, though this is a
OL,21,Flong and difficult journey.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G9/13
