OL,3,CFailings found in care of man who
OL,4,Ckilled his father after escaping from
OL,5,Chospital
OL,7,F"Our family remain astounded by the
OL,8,Flack of compassion, insight or
OL,9,Freflection of the health board and the
OL,10,FCity and County of Swansea given the
OL,11,Ffailings set out by the coroner, some
OL,12,Fof which contributed to Kim's death.
OL,14,F"They care for the most vulnerable in
OL,15,Fsociety and yet it took Kim's death to
OL,16,Ffinally get (Dan) the care he so
OL,17,Fdesperately needed and deserved."
