OL,7,FA statement from Swansea Bay
OL,8,FUniversity Health Board, issued after
OL,9,Fthe inquest, said: "This is an
OL,10,Fextremely harrowing and tragic case
OL,11,Fand we fully acknowledge the distress
OL,12,Fand anguish felt by Dr Harrison's
OL,13,Ffamily and friends.
OL,15,F"We offer our unequivocal apologies
OL,16,Ffor our failings in this case, and are
OL,17,Fdetermined to learn and do everything
OL,18,Fpossible to avoid anything like this
OL,19,Fhappening again.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                  G11/13
