OL,7,F"We recognise that insights and
OL,8,Finformation provided by family members
OL,9,Fabout patients play a crucial role in
OL,10,Fplanning and delivering care. We have
OL,11,Fstrengthened our processes around
OL,12,Fensuring this vital information is
OL,13,Frobustly recorded and shared with
OL,14,Fclinical teams.
OL,16,F"A number of key actions are in
OL,17,Fprocess, including additional security
OL,18,Fmeasures being built into the Ward F
OL,19,Fat Neath Port Talbot Hospital which
OL,20,Fprovide extra locked areas around exit
OL,21,Fdoors.
